title: Gwjwn sudem bwi swrgw-ao
lyrics:
Gwjwn sudem bwi swrgw-ao
Arphofra dinwi rongzadwng -2
(A)
Dukhuni lwithw khou nwng derhananwi
Swrgw Bifani thangki jafung hwbai -2
Bekainw dinwi swrgw Bifaya
Dor khou kheonan hwbai -2
(B)
Gwjwn hwnan jwngkhou banjainanwi
Swrgw Bifani serao dwnnw thakwi -2
Thangbai nwng bwi gwjwn swrgwao
Bifanw khwnta hwinw -2
